<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard Marketing | ClickUp Abril</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-2.27.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

    <style>
        body { 
            background-color: #070A12; 
            color: #FAFAFA; 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        /* Estilos tipo "Glassmorphism" (cristal oscuro) */
        .glass-card {
            background-color: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            padding: 1.25rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Estilos del slider (barra de presupuesto) */
        input[type=range] {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            width: 100%;
            background: transparent;
        }
        input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            height: 20px;
            width: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #e879f9; /* fuchsia-400 */
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -8px;
        }
        input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-runnable-track {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 9999px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen relative text-white">

    <div class="pointer-events-none fixed inset-0 overflow-hidden z-0">
        <div class="absolute -top-40 left-1/2 h-[520px] w-[520px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500/15 blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-48 -left-24 h-[520px] w-[520px] rounded-full bg-cyan-500/15 blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-[520px] w-[520px] rounded-full bg-violet-500/15 blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-8 md:px-6">
        
        <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
            <div>
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-white/70">
                    <i data-lucide="layout-dashboard" class="h-4 w-4 text-white/80"></i>
                    Dashboard Marketing, ClickUp "Abril Contenido"
                </div>
                <h1 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Panel Interactivo para justificar inversión fuerte en Ads</h1>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/65">Enfoque PM + CMO: visibiliza capacidad de producción (ClickUp funnel), detecta cuellos de botella y proyecta ROI al escalar presupuesto.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card !p-4 max-w-xs">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-2">
                        <i data-lucide="sparkles" class="h-5 w-5 text-fuchsia-300"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-xs text-white/60">Lectura ejecutiva</p>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white" id="narrative-text">Tenemos inventario creativo robusto...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 mb-6">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/20 via-cyan-500/15 to-violet-500/15"></div>
                <div class="relative flex justify-between gap-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-2"><i data-lucide="trending-up" class="h-5 w-5 text-white/90"></i></div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Tasa de productividad</p>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white" id="kpi-prod">38% (30/80)</p>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-white/60">Tarjetas completadas vs total mensual</p>
